data.description: Beautiful One-Story Jefferson model in the highly coveted Mountainview Village on the northern end of Sun City Anthem.  The courtyard entry leads to a spacious floor plan that features a large great room with separate dining areas, split 2 bedroom plan, and laminate flooring throughout. The eat-in kitchen is equipped with a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances including a wine fridge. Primary Bedroom has a large built out closet, double sinks and shower. Ceiling fans, shutters, crown molding plus washer and dryer included! Mature low-maintenance landscaping, with an oversized lot with a covered patio ideal for entertaining, synthetic grass, pavers and no neighbors behind. Insulated 2 car garage with cabinets and water softener.  Sun City Anthem is an age-restricted community featuring a community and recreation center, fitness facilities, a social calendar, and more! Walking distance to the grocery store, pharmacy, and restaurants.
